lead_paragraph: Adelaide United claimed a long-awaited A-League title on Sunday with a nerve-jangling 3-1 win that consigned the Western Sydney Wanderers to a third dose of heartbreak in the Australian championship decider.

headline.print_headline: Adelaide End Long Wait for A-League Title Triumph
headline.main: Adelaide End Long Wait for A-League Title Triumph
